node.text:
I'm honored to be debuting my new logo on the Air Jordan 36. I know what @jumpman23 brand stands for and I’m proud to represent it. 

Check out more about the design on AIR.JORDAN.Com & don’t forget to look tomorrow only in the Nike App (check your geo for availability). Can't wait to get these on the court #itslightwork

node.text: It’s definitely not easy. We fought till the end! What a pleasure has been playing for my country in 1st Olympics ever for us!!! So proud of these guys! And thank you Slovenians for supporting us every game!! 🇸🇮🇸🇮🇸🇮🇸🇮🇸🇮❤️❤️❤️❤️
